 \lim_{t \to x} \frac{f(t,y,g(\overset{\downarrow}{t},y)) - f(x,y,g(x,y))}{t-x} = \frac{\partial h(x,y)}{\partial x} 
 \lim_{t \to x} \frac{f(t,y,g(\overset{\downarrow}{x},y)) - f(x,y,g(x,y))}{t-x} = \left. \frac{\partial f(x,y,z)}{\partial x} \right|_{z = g(x,y)} 
